在月球表面上用肉眼可以清楚看見有黑暗的，相對平坦的平原，我们称之为[[月海|月海]]，這是因為古代的天文學家認為这些地方充滿了[[水|水]]<ref>{{Cite book|title=Observing the Moon|author=Wlasuk, Peter|publisher=Springer|year=2000|page=19|isbn=1852331933|url=http://books.google.com/?id=TWtLIOlPwS4C&pg=PT30}}</ref>。現在，我們知道这些黑暗部分是古代火山爆发后熔岩浆在窪地凝結成的廣大[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]。和地球的玄武岩類似，月海中的玄武岩含有豐富的鐵，而完全缺乏因水流過而出现的礦物<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/April04/lunarAnorthosites.html|title = The Oldest Moon Rocks|last = Norman|first = M.|publisher = Planetary Science Research Discoveries|date = 2004-04-21|accessdate = 2007-04-12|archive-date = 2007-04-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070418152325/http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/April04/lunarAnorthosites.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last = Varricchio|first = L.|title = Inconstant Moon|publisher = Xlibris Books|year = 2006|isbn = 1-59926-393-9}}</ref>。大多數噴發的熔岩浆流入與[[撞击坑|撞擊盆地]]相連接的窪地，形成月海。现在科学家已经在月球正面的月海中發現幾個拥有[[盾狀火山|盾狀火山]]和火山穹頂的地質分區<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Head|first = L.W.J.W.|title = Lunar Gruithuisen and Mairan domes: Rheology and mode of emplacement|journal = Journal of Geophysical Research|year = 2003|volume = 108|url = http://www.agu.org/pubs/crossref/2003/2002JE001909.shtml|accessdate = 2007-04-12|doi = 10.1029/2002JE001909|pages = 5012|bibcode = 2003JGRE..108.5012W|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070312071105/http://www.agu.org/pubs/crossref/2003/2002JE001909.shtml|archivedate = 2007-03-12}}</ref>，这些是熔岩浆凝結形成月海的证据。

幾乎所有的月海都位于月球正面，占正面面積的31%<ref name="worldbook"/>，相較之下，在月球背面只有少數的月海，只涵蓋了背面2%的面積<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Gillis|first = J.J.|coauthors = Spudis, P.D.|title = The Composition and Geologic Setting of Lunar Far Side Maria|journal = Lunar and Planetary Science|year = 1996|volume = 27|pages = 413–404|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996LPI....27..413G|accessdate = 2007-04-12|archive-date = 2019-06-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190628161416/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996LPI....27..413G|dead-url = no}}</ref>。這被認為和通过[[月球探勘者|月球探勘者]]的伽瑪射線光譜儀所描绘的月球化學圖上所看見在月球正面地殼下的[[克里普礦物|生熱元素的濃縮]]有关。生熱元素的濃縮會造成地函下的溫度上升，部分熔解，并上升到表面造成噴發<ref name="S06">{{Cite journal|last = Shearer|first = C.|coauthors = ''et al.''|title = Thermal and magmatic evolution of the Moon|journal = Reviews in Mineralogy and Geochemistry|volume = 60|pages = 365–518|year = 2006|doi = 10.2138/rmg.2006.60.4}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/281/5382/1484|title=Global Elemental Maps of the Moon: The Lunar Prospector Gamma-Ray Spectrometer|author=Lawrence, D. J. ''et al.''|journal=Science|volume=281|issue=5382|pages=1484–1489|doi=10.1126/science.281.5382.1484|issn=1095-9203|publisher=HighWire Press|date=1998-08-11|accessdate=2009-08-29|pmid=9727970|bibcode=1998Sci...281.1484L|archive-date=2009-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090516065007/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/281/5382/1484|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/Aug00/newMoon.html|title = A New Moon for the Twenty-First Century|last = Taylor|first = G.J.|publisher = Planetary Science Research Discoveries, Hawai'i Institute of Geophysics and Planetology|date = 2000-08-31|accessdate = 2007-04-12|archive-date = 2020-05-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200519181414/http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/Aug00/newMoon.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。大部分[[月海|玄武岩]]的噴發都出現在30至35億年前的[[月球地質年代|雨海紀]]，但也有少部分样本的辐射定年显示其形成于更古老的42亿年<ref name="Papike">{{Cite journal|last = Papike|first = J.|coauthors = Ryder, G.; Shearer, C.|title = Lunar Samples|journal = Reviews in Mineralogy and Geochemistry|volume = 36|pages = 5.1–5.234|year = 1998}}</ref>，也有一些相对年轻的样品，最年輕的噴發物經由[[撞擊坑計數|撞擊坑計數]]测定年限发现其发生在12億年前<ref name="Hiesinger">{{Cite journal|last = Hiesinger|first = H.|coauthors = Head, J.W.; Wolf, U.; Jaumanm, R.; Neukum, G.|title = Ages and stratigraphy of mare basalts in Oceanus Procellarum, Mare Numbium, Mare Cognitum, and Mare Insularum|journal = J. Geophys. Res.|volume = 108|pages = 1029|year = 2003|doi = 10.1029/2002JE001985|bibcode = 2003JGRE..108.5065H }}</ref>。

月球上較亮的部分被稱為“高地”，因為它們高於大多數的月海。經由輻射定年測定它們是於44億年前形成的，这意味着这些高地可能是在[[月球岩漿海|月球岩漿海]]形成时的[[斜長岩|斜長岩]]堆積所产生的<ref name="Papike"/><ref name="Hiesinger"/>。月球上沒有任何一個主要的山脈被认为由地质構造事件产生的，这和地球的情况刚好相反<ref>{{Cite web|last = Munsell|first = K.|publisher = NASA|work = Solar System Exploration|title = Majestic Mountains|url = http://sse.jpl.nasa.gov/educ/themes/display.cfm?Item=mountains|date = 2006-12-04|accessdate = 2007-04-12|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080917055643/http://sse.jpl.nasa.gov/educ/themes/display.cfm?Item=mountains|archivedate = 2008-09-17}}</ref>。
==== 撞擊坑 ====
{{See also|月球環形山列表}}平均每天月球都會承受超過3噸宇宙物質的撞擊<ref>{{Cite web |title=小行星撞月球畫面曝光 「眩彩如煙火」每天承受3噸星體撞擊 |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E8%A1%8C%E6%98%9F%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%9C%A9%E5%BD%A9%E5%A6%82%E7%85%99%E7%81%AB-%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%89%BF%E5%8F%973%E5%99%B8%E6%98%9F%E9%AB%94%E6%92%9E%E6%93%8A-101208842.html |website=tw.news.yahoo.com |language=zh-TW |access-date=2022-06-19 |archive-date=2021-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205050340/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E8%A1%8C%E6%98%9F%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%9C%A9%E5%BD%A9%E5%A6%82%E7%85%99%E7%81%AB-%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%89%BF%E5%8F%973%E5%99%B8%E6%98%9F%E9%AB%94%E6%92%9E%E6%93%8A-101208842.html }}</ref>，當中的[[小行星|小行星]]或[[彗星|彗星]]撞擊月球表面時會形成[[撞击坑|撞擊坑]]，是另一個主要會影響月球表面地形的主要地質事件<ref>{{Cite book|title = Impact cratering: A geologic process|url = https://archive.org/details/impactcrateringg0000melo|last = Melosh|first = H. J.|publisher = Oxford Univ. Press|year = 1989|isbn = 0195042840}}</ref>。现在估計单在月球正面直徑大於1公里的隕石坑就大約有300,000個<ref>{{Cite web|title=Moon Facts|url=http://planck.esa.int/science-e/www/object/index.cfm?fobjectid=31412|work=SMART-1|publisher=European Space Agency|year=2010|accessdate=2010-05-12|archive-date=2012-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317004513/http://planck.esa.int/science-e/www/object/index.cfm?fobjectid=31412|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中有些隕石坑以知名的學者、科學家、藝術家和探險家的名字[[月面學#月面圖和月球地名|命名]]<ref name="gazetteer">{{Cite web|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/append6.html#Moon|title=Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature: Categories for Naming Features on Planets and Satellites|publisher=U.S. Geological Survey|accessdate=2010-04-08|archive-date=2007-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824115900/http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/append6.html#Moon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[月球地質年代|月球地質年代]]是根据月面上的重大陨石撞击事件进行分界，包括在[[酒海紀|酒海]]、[[早雨海世|雨海]]和[[東方海|東方海]]等的撞击事件。这些撞击事件的結構特徵是产生多層物質隆起的環，通常是由數百至數千公里直徑的圍裙状噴發物沉積形成一個區域性的[[地層學|地層視界]]<ref name="geologic">{{Cite journal |first=Don |last=Wilhelms |year=1987 |title=Geologic History of the Moon |publisher=U.S. Geological Survey |url=http://ser.sese.asu.edu/GHM/ghm_07txt.pdf |chapter=Relative Ages |journal= |access-date=2011-01-31 |archive-date=2010-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611054723/http://ser.sese.asu.edu/GHM/ghm_07txt.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于月球没有大氣層、天氣变化，在最近几十亿年也没有地質活動，大部分環形山都保存得很完好。雖然有幾個多環盆地明顯的已經很久遠，它們還是能用於分派相對的年齡。由於撞擊坑是以恆定的速率累積，計算單位面積內的撞擊坑數目可以用來估計表面的年齡<ref name=geologic/>。[[阿波罗计划|阿波羅任務]]收集撞擊熔化的岩石以輻射測定年齡，群集在38億和41億年的年齡：這已被用來解释撞擊的[[後期重轟炸期|後期重轟炸期]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Hartmann |first=William K. |last2=Quantin |first2=Cathy |last3=Mangold |first3=Nicolas |year=2007 |volume=186 |pages=11–23 |journal=Icarus |title=Possible long-term decline in impact rates: 2. Lunar impact-melt data regarding impact history |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2006.09.009 |postscript=<!--None--> |bibcode = 2007Icar..186...11H }}</ref>。

覆蓋在月球地殼上的是高度[[粉碎|粉碎的]]（碎裂成更小的顆粒）和[[撞擊花園|撞擊園藝]]下的表面層稱為[[表岩屑|風化層]]，是由撞擊過程形成的。最細微的風化層，是[[二氧化硅|二氧化矽]]的[[月球土壤|月球土壤]]玻璃狀物體，有著像雪一樣的紋理和聞起來像用過的[[火药|火藥]]<ref>{{Cite web|date = 2006-01-30|accessdate = 2010-03-15|url = http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2006/30jan_smellofmoondust.htm|title = The Smell of Moondust|publisher = NASA|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100308112332/http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2006/30jan_smellofmoondust.htm|archivedate = 2010-03-08}}</ref>。較老的風化層表面一般比年輕的表面厚；在高地的厚度在10-20米之間，在海的厚度則是3-5米。<ref>{{Cite book|last = Heiken|first = G.|coauthors = Vaniman, D.; French, B. (eds.) |year = 1991 |title = Lunar Sourcebook, a user's guide to the Moon|url = https://archive.org/details/lunarsourcebooku00heik|publisher = Cambridge University Press|location = New York|pages = [https://archive.org/details/lunarsourcebooku00heik/page/n774 736]|isbn = 0521334446}}</ref>
在細緻的粉碎風化層下面是“粗風化層（megaregolith）”，厚達數公里高度碎裂的基岩<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Rasmussen|first = K.L.|coauthors = Warren, P.H.|title = Megaregolith thickness, heat flow, and the bulk composition of the Moon|journal = Nature|year = 1985|volume = 313|pages = 121–124|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1985Natur.313..121R|accessdate = 2007-04-12|doi = 10.1038/313121a0|bibcode = 1985Natur.313..121R|archive-date = 2007-10-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071011094411/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1985Natur.313..121R|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 表面地質 ===
{{Main|月球地質}}
[[File:1-250万月球全月地质图.jpg|居中]]制作的1:250万月球全月地质图]]
[[File:Composition_of_lunar_soil.png|缩略图]]
月球表面的[[化学元素|化学元素]]分布极不均。按照其[[丰度|丰度]]依次为：[[氧|氧]]、[[硅|硅]]、[[铁|铁]]、[[镁|镁]]、[[钙|钙]]、[[铝|铝]]、[[锰|锰]]、[[钛|钛]]。氧的含量估计为42%（按重量）。[[碳|碳]]和[[氮|氮]]只有痕迹，似乎只存在于[[太阳风|太阳风]]带来的微量沉积中，[[氢|氢]]主要集中在月球的[[天體的極|两极]]<ref>{{cite web|title=《月球表面氢的分布》|url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2003/pdf/1867.pdf|author=S. Maurice|format=PDF|access-date=2011-01-25|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905223117/https://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2003/pdf/1867.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
====月岩====
{{main|月岩}}
月球表面主要有四类[[岩石|岩石]]：月海[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]、高地岩石（主要包括[[斜长岩|斜长岩]]与富镁的结晶岩套）、[[克里普矿物|克里普岩]]和[[角砾岩|角砾岩]]，且分布不均。
====月壤====
{{main|月壤}}
月壤是[[月球|月球]]表面的[[粒径|细微]][[表岩屑|表岩屑]]，主要是[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]和[[斜长岩|斜长岩]]物理崩解的结果，由多年来持续的[[撞击事件|流星撞击]]和太阳及星际带电粒子轰击所造成。

=== 內部構造 ===
{{Main|月球內部構造}}
[[File:Moon_diagram.svg|thumb]]
月球是一个已經[[行星分異|分異]]的天體，即它拥有[[地壳|地殼]]、[[地幔|地函]]、和[[行星核心|核心]]。月球的內核富含固態鐵，半徑大約为240公里，此外還有一個流體的外核，主要成分是液態鐵，半徑大約为300公里。核心周圍是部分熔融的邊界層，約有500公里的宽度<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/topics/moonmars/features/lunar_core.html|title=NASA - NASA Research Team Reveals Moon Has Earth-Like Core|work=nasa.gov|access-date=2011-01-31|archive-date=2012-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111112210/http://www.nasa.gov/topics/moonmars/features/lunar_core.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>邊界層結構是在45億年前月球形成不久之後，由[[月球岩漿海|月球岩漿海]]通過分離結晶形成的<ref>{{Cite journal|doi = 10.1038/ngeo417|title =Timing of crystallization of the lunar magma ocean constrained by the oldest zircon|year = 2009|last1 = Nemchin|first1 = A.|last2 = Timms|first2 = N.|last3 = Pidgeon|first3 = R.|last4 = Geisler|first4 = T.|last5 = Reddy|first5 = S.|last6 = Meyer|first6 = C.|journal = Nature Geoscience|volume = 2|pages = 133–136 |bibcode = 2009NatGe...2..133N }}</ref>。岩漿海的結晶可以經由[[沉澱|沉澱]]形成由[[鎂鐵質|鎂鐵質]]和沉積的[[橄欖石|橄欖石]]、[[辉石|斜輝石]]和[[辉石|斜方輝石]]等礦物组成的地函。四分之三的岩漿海結晶之後，可能形成密度較低的[[斜長石|斜長石]]并浮在地殼的頂部<ref name="S06"/>。最後才由液體結晶的部分會被夾在地殼和地函之間，並且含有大量[[形式系统相容性|不相容]]和發熱的元素<ref name="W06"/>和之相符的是從月球軌道上遥感繪製的月球地質化學圖也顯示其地殼幾乎都是由[[斜長岩|斜長岩]]组成<ref name="L06">{{Cite journal|last = Lucey|first = P.|coauthors = ''et al.'' |title = Understanding the lunar surface and space-Moon interactions|journal = Reviews in Mineralogy and Geochemistry|volume = 60|pages = 83–219|year = 2006 |doi = 10.2138/rmg.2006.60.2}}</ref>。通过对部分熔融的地函噴發出的熔岩流冷凝下来的[[月岩|月岩]]樣本的研究，科学家確認地函含有比地球更豐富的鐵，其主要成分是鎂鐵質<ref name="W06"/>。通过地球物理技術发现月球地殼的平均厚度約為50公里左右<ref name="W06">{{Cite journal|last = Wieczorek|first = M.|coauthors = ''et al.''|title = The constitution and structure of the lunar interior|journal = Reviews in Mineralogy and Geochemistry|volume = 60|pages = 221–364|year = 2006|doi = 10.2138/rmg.2006.60.3}}</ref>。

月球是太陽系內密度第二高的衛星，仅次于[[木卫一|木衛一埃歐]]<ref name="Schubert2004">{{Cite book|last=Schubert |first=J. ''et al.'' |editor=F. Bagenal ''et al.'' |title=Jupiter: The Planet, Satellites, and Magnetosphere |year=2004 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |pages=281–306 |isbn=978-0521818087 |chapter=Interior composition, structure, and dynamics of the Galilean satellites. }}</ref>。但是月球的內核並不大，半徑大約是350公里甚至更小<ref name="W06"/>，只佔月球大小的約20%，相較之下，其它[[类地行星|地球型天體]]的比例約為50%。它的組成尚不是完全清楚，可能是由金屬鐵组成，同时含有少量[[硫|硫]]和[[镍|鎳]]。对月球隨著時間變化轉動的分析顯示月球核心至少仍有部分是熔融的<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Williams|first = J.G.|coauthors = Turyshev, S.G.; Boggs, D.H.; Ratcliff, J.T.|title = Lunar laser ranging science: Gravitational physics and lunar interior and geodesy|journal = Advances in Space Research|year = 2006|volume = 37|issue = 1|pages = 6771|url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1987AREPS..15..271S|doi = 10.1016/j.asr.2005.05.013|arxiv = gr-qc/0412049|bibcode = 2006AdSpR..37...67W|access-date = 2011-01-30|archive-date = 2012-03-16|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66CTLxZOa?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1987AREPS..15..271S|dead-url = no}}</ref>。
=== 重力和磁場 ===
[[File:MareSmithiiTG.jpg|thumb]]的[[测绘学|测绘圖]]（上圖）及對應之[[引力|引力圖]]（下圖）顯示，这个地方有一個和地形相反的質量瘤。]]
月球表面的引力约为地球的六分之一。月球的重力場已经通过围绕月球旋转的探测器發射无线电信号的[[多普勒效应|-{zh-hans:多普勒效应;zh-hk:多普勒效應;zh-tw:都卜勒效應;}-]]所測量的。月球重力場主要的特徵是拥有[[質量瘤|质量瘤]]，即在一些巨大的[[撞击坑|撞擊盆地]]却反而出现较重的重力分布，这可能與组成这些盆地的玄武岩熔岩流密度较大有關係<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Muller|first = P.|coauthors = Sjogren, W.|title = Mascons: lunar mass concentrations|journal = Science|volume = 161 |pages = 680–684|year = 1968|doi = 10.1126/science.161.3842.680|pmid = 17801458|issue = 3842|bibcode = 1968Sci...161..680M }}</ref>，這些異常對環繞月球軌道的太空船有極大的影響，如果经月球这些地域时，假如太空船与月面距离足够低，而且轨道不加修正的话，那么太空船会在数个月或数年间在月球表面坠毁。但令人困惑的是，熔岩流密度本身不足以完全解釋重力异常，有一些質量瘤的存在明显和月海中的火山作用形成的熔岩流无关<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Konopliv|first = A.|coauthors = Asmar, S.; Carranza, E.; Sjogren, W.; Yuan, D.|title = Recent gravity models as a result of the Lunar Prospector mission|journal = Icarus|volume = 50|pages = 1–18|year = 2001|doi = 10.1006/icar.2000.6573|bibcode = 2001Icar..150....1K }}</ref>。

月球拥有一個強度不到[[地磁场|地球磁場]]百分之一，範圍在1至數百[[特斯拉|特士拉]]之间的外在[[磁場|磁場]]。月球上已被发现有类似质量瘤的异常的磁场区。这些磁场区有明显不同于其他地方的磁场强度（'''''但是原因未知'''''）。
天体液體金屬核心可以生成的全球性[[雙極|雙極性]]磁場，但现在
月球的磁場并不是由液體金屬核心产生的，而可能是在月球演化的歷史早期被磁化而一直保留至今的地殼磁場<ref name="GB2009">{{Cite journal|doi=10.1126/science.1166804|last1=Garrick-Bethell|first1=Ian|first2=iBenjamin P. |last2=Weiss|first3= David L. |last3=Shuster|first4= Jennifer |last4=Buz|year=2009|title=Early Lunar Magnetism|journal=Science|volume=323|issue=5912|pages=356–359|pmid=19150839|bibcode = 2009Sci...323..356G }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://lunar.arc.nasa.gov/results/magelres.htm|publisher = Lunar Prospector (NASA)|title = Magnetometer / Electron Reflectometer Results|year = 2001|accessdate = 2010-03-17|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527121330/http://lunar.arc.nasa.gov/results/magelres.htm|archivedate = 2010-05-27}}</ref>，月球磁场另一種可能来源是在大碰撞事件期間生成的瞬態磁場殘餘的磁化，通過撞擊產生的電漿雲包圍，擴大了磁場的范围，这种说法受到最大的地殼磁場撞擊盆地對面出現[[對蹠點|對蹠點]]的支持<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Hood|first = L.L.|coauthors = Huang, Z.|title = Formation of magnetic anomalies antipodal to lunar impact basins: Two-dimensional model calculations|journal = J. Geophys. Res.|volume = 96|pages = 9837–9846|year = 1991|doi = 10.1029/91JB00308|bibcode = 1991JGR....96.9837H }}</ref>。

=== 大氣層 ===
{{Main|月球大氣層}}
月球有一個非常稀薄、接近[[真空|真空]]的大氣層，總質量低於10公噸<ref>{{Cite book| editor = Richard D. Johnson & Charles Holbrow| last = Globus| first = Ruth| title = Space Settlements: A Design Study| chapter = Chapter 5, Appendix J: Impact Upon Lunar Atmosphere| publisher = NASA| url = http://settlement.arc.nasa.gov/75SummerStudy/5appendJ.html| year = 1977| accessdate = 2010-03-17| archive-date = 2010-05-31| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100531205037/http://settlement.arc.nasa.gov/75SummerStudy/5appendJ.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。如此小的大气質量在月球表面產生的壓力大約是3{{esp|−15}}[[大氣壓|atm]]（0.3[[奈巴l|nPa]]），数值随着月球一天的时间不同而改变。月球大气的來源包括[[出氣|出氣]]和[[溅射|濺射]]，如[[太阳风|太陽風]]的離子轟極月球表面釋放出的原子<ref name="L06"/><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Crotts |first=Arlin P.S. |title=Lunar Outgassing, Transient Phenomena and The Return to The Moon, I: Existing Data. |year=2008 |publisher=Department of Astronomy, Columbia University |url=http://www.astro.columbia.edu/~arlin/TLP/paper1.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2009-09-29 |journal= |archive-date=2009-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220081142/http://www.astro.columbia.edu/~arlin/TLP/paper1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。过往曾經檢測到由濺射產生的原子包括[[钠|鈉]]和[[钾|鉀]]，相同的情况也曾在[[水星|水星]]和[[木卫一|木衛一埃歐]]的大氣中發現過。月球大气的[[氦|氦-4]]來自太陽風，[[氩|氬-40]]、[[氡|氡-222]]和[[钋|釙-210]]则來自月球地函相关元素[[放射性|放射性衰變]]後的濺射<ref name="Stern1999"/><ref>{{Cite journal|last = Lawson|first = S.|coauthors = Feldman, W.; Lawrence, D.; Moore, K.; Elphic, R.; Belian, R.|title = Recent outgassing from the lunar surface: the Lunar Prospector alpha particle spectrometer|journal = J. Geophys. Res.|volume = 110|pages=1029|year = 2005|doi = 10.1029/2005JE002433|bibcode = 2005JGRE..110.9009L }}</ref>。但月球大气中缺乏存在於月球[[表岩屑|表岩屑]]的[[氧|氧]]、[[氮|氮]]、[[碳|碳]]、[[氢|氫]]和[[镁|鎂]]等自然元素的原子或分子，目前原因尚不清楚<ref name="Stern1999">{{Cite journal|last = Stern|first = S.A.|title = The Lunar atmosphere: History, status, current problems, and context|journal = Rev. Geophys.|volume = 37|year = 1999|pages = 453–491|doi = 10.1029/1999RG900005|bibcode = 1999RvGeo..37..453S }}</ref>。[[月船1号|月船1號]]已經在月球大气中發現水蒸氣的存在，其含量隨著月球纬度的不同而改變，大約在纬度为60-70度时水蒸气的含量最高。这些水蒸气可能是由月球表面表岩屑的水冰[[升华|升華]]而生成的<ref name="Sridharan2010">{{Cite journal|last=Sridharan|first=R.|coauthors=S.M. Ahmed, Tirtha Pratim Dasa, P. Sreelathaa, P. Pradeepkumara, Neha Naika, and Gogulapati Supriya|year=2010|pages=947|volume=58|title=‘Direct’ evidence for water (H2O) in the sunlit lunar ambience from CHACE on MIP of Chandrayaan I |journal=Planetary and Space Science|doi=10.1016/j.pss.2010.02.013|bibcode = 2010P&SS...58..947S }}</ref>。月球大气层的氣體有些被月球的重力吸引回到表岩屑，有些由于太陽的輻射壓，或者被太陽風的電離後逃逸到太空中<ref name="Stern1999"/>。

=== 季節 ===
月球的轉軸傾角只有1.54°，遠小於地球的23.44°。由於這個緣故，太陽照射對月球季節變化的影響很小，反而是月球表面地形对季節变化有重要作用<ref name=bbc/>。在2004年，[[约翰·霍普金斯大学|约翰·霍普金斯大学]]的Ben Bussey博士率領的小組研究克萊芒蒂娜探测器在1994年獲得的影像，發現位于月球北極的[[皮爾斯_(火山口)|皮爾斯環形山]]邊緣有4個区域在整個月球日中都被陽光所照亮，形成[[永晝峰|永晝峰]]，而在月球南極地区沒有类似的区域。而在極區的許多環形山底部是永久黑暗的，没有受到阳光照射<ref name="M03">{{Cite web|url = http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/June03/lunarShadows.html|title = The Moon's Dark, Icy Poles|last = Martel|first = L.M.V.|publisher = Planetary Science Research Discoveries, Hawai'i Institute of Geophysics and Planetology|date = 2003-06-04|accessdate = 2007-04-12|archive-date = 2012-03-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120301090706/http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/June03/lunarShadows.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。這些黑暗的環形山底部是極低溫的：[[月球勘測軌道飛行器|月球勘測軌道飛行器]]在夏天的南極環形山底部測得的最低溫度是35K（−238 °C）<ref>{{Cite web|date=2009-09-17|url=http://www.diviner.ucla.edu/blog/?p=123|title=Diviner News|publisher=UCLA|accessdate=2010-03-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307031354/http://www.diviner.ucla.edu/blog/?p=123|archivedate=2010-03-07}}</ref>，而在接近冬至时在北極測得[[埃尔米特环形山|埃尔米特环形山]]的溫度只有26K（−247 °C）。這个温度比[[冥王星|冥王星]]的表面溫度還要低，是太空船在太陽系中所測得的最低溫度<ref name="bbc">{{Cite news|title='Coldest place' found on the Moon|publisher=BBC News|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/8416749.stm|author=Jonathan Amos|accessdate=2010-03-20|date=2009-12-16|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811182717/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/8416749.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
=== 水的存在 ===
{{Main|月球的水}}
[[File:Moon_South_Pole.jpg|thumbnail]]拍攝的月球南極馬賽克圖：請注意極地的永久陰影。]] 

月球的表面不存在液態水，因為太陽輻射會使水被[[光解|光解]]并快速逸入太空。但從1960年代以來，科學家假設由[[彗星|彗星]]撞擊所帶來的水、或者來自[[太阳风|太陽風]]的氫和含氧豐富的月岩反應所產生的水，都可能以冰的型態沉積下來，并在月球兩極撞擊坑低溫的永久陰影區留下可以追蹤得到的痕跡<ref name="Margot1999">{{Cite journal
|author=Margot, J. L.; Campbell, D. B.; Jurgens, R. F.; Slade, M. A.
|title=Topography of the Lunar Poles from Radar Interferometry: A Survey of Cold Trap Locations
|journal=Science|date=1999-06-04|volume=284
|issue=5420|pages=1658–1660
|doi=10.1126/science.284.5420.1658
|pmid=10356393 |bibcode = 1999Sci...284.1658M }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal
|first=William R.|last=Ward
|title=Past Orientation of the Lunar Spin Axis
|journal=Science|date=1975-08-01|volume=189
|issue=4200|pages=377–379
|doi=10.1126/science.189.4200.377
|pmid=17840827 |bibcode = 1975Sci...189..377W }}</ref>。電腦模擬月面的永久陰影區約有14,000平方公里<ref name="M03"/>。在月球上可用水的數量是一個重要的因素，可以決定建設一個[[月球殖民|月球適居區]]計畫的成本效益，因為從地球運水到月球的費用極為昂貴<ref name="seedhouse2009">{{Cite book|last=Seedhouse|first=Erik|title=Lunar Outpost: The Challenges of Establishing a Human Settlement on the Moon|publisher=Springer Praxis|location=Germany|year=2009|series=Springer-Praxis Books in Space Exploration|page=136|isbn=0387097465|url=http://books.google.com/?id=ZJm_i3GS4r4C&pg=PA136}}</ref>。

近年來，已經在月球表面發現水的特徵<ref name="moonwater_18032010">{{Cite web|url=http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2010/18mar_moonwater.htm?list940097|title=The Multiplying Mystery of Moonwater|last=Coulter|first=Dauna|date=2010-03-18|publisher=Science@NASA|accessdate=2010-03-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160516155030/http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2010/18mar_moonwater.htm?list940097|archivedate=2016-05-16}}</ref>。在1994年，安裝在[[克萊芒蒂娜_(太空船)|克萊門汀號]]太空船的[[克萊芒蒂娜任務#雙向雷達實驗|雙向雷達實驗]]，顯示有少量、冰凍的水存在接近表面的凹穴內。但是，後續使用[[阿雷西博天文台|阿雷西博天文台]]的雷達觀測，又認為此一發現可能是由新撞擊坑中的岩石近被撞擊的岩石噴出的<ref>{{Cite web|last = Spudis|first = P.|title = Ice on the Moon|url = http://www.thespacereview.com/article/740/1|publisher = The Space Review|date = 2006-11-06|accessdate = 2007-04-12|archive-date = 2007-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070222083000/http://www.thespacereview.com/article/740/1|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在1998年，月球勘探者攜帶的[[月球勘探者#中子能譜計(NS)|中子能譜計]]顯示，在極地附近深度1米的風化層存在著高濃度的氫<ref name="Feldman1998">{{Cite journal|last=Feldman|first=W. C.|coauthors=S. Maurice,  A. B. Binder,  B. L. Barraclough,  R. C. Elphic,  D. J. Lawrence  |year=1998|title=Fluxes of Fast and Epithermal Neutrons from Lunar Prospector: Evidence for Water Ice at the Lunar Poles|journal=Science|pmid=9727973|volume=281|issue=5382|pages=1496–1500|doi=10.1126/science.281.5382.1496|bibcode = 1998Sci...281.1496F }}</ref>。在2008年，對一顆由阿波羅15號帶回的熔岩珠的分析，顯示有微量的水存在於球状硅酸盐玻璃內<ref name="Saal2008">{{Cite journal|last=Saal|first=Alberto E.|coauthors=Hauri, Erik H.; Cascio, Mauro L.; van Orman, James A.; Rutherford, Malcolm C.; Cooper, Reid F.|year=2008|title=Volatile content of lunar volcanic glasses and the presence of water in the Moon's interior|journal=Nature|pmid=18615079|volume=454|issue=7201|pages=192–195|doi=10.1038/nature07047|bibcode = 2008Natur.454..192S }}</ref>。

在2008年，印度的''[[月船1号|月船1號]]''太空船使用在載[[月球礦物繪圖儀|月球礦物繪圖儀]]確認表面有水冰的存在。分光計觀測在反射的陽光中偵測到[[羟基|羥基]]的通用吸收譜線，提供了有大量水冰在月球表面的證據。太空船顯示濃度可能高達1000[[百萬分之|PPM]]<ref name="Pieters2009">{{Cite journal|doi=10.1126/science.1178658|last=Pieters|first=C. M.|coauthors=Goswami, J. N.; Clark, R. N.; Annadurai, M.; Boardman, J.; Buratti, B.; Combe, J.-P.; Dyar, M. D.; Green, R.; Head, J. W.; Hibbitts, C.; Hicks, M.; Isaacson, P.; Klima, R.; Kramer, G.; Kumar, S.; Livo, E.; Lundeen, S.; Malaret, E.; McCord, T.; Mustard, J.; Nettles, J.; Petro, N.; Runyon, C.; Staid, M.; Sunshine, J.; Taylor, L. A.; Tompkins, S.; Varanasi, P.|year=2009|title=Character and Spatial Distribution of OH/H2O on the Surface of the Moon Seen by M3 on Chandrayaan-1|journal=Science|volume=326|issue=5952|pages=568–72|pmid=19779151|bibcode = 2009Sci...326..568P }}</ref>。在2009年，''[[月球坑观测和传感卫星|月球坑觀測和傳感衛星]]''送了一個2,300公斤的撞擊器到極區永久陰暗的環形山，並且從噴出的羽狀物質中至少檢測到100公斤的水<ref name="Planetary">{{Cite web|url=http://planetary.org/news/2009/1113_LCROSS_Lunar_Impactor_Mission_Yes_We.html|title=LCROSS Lunar Impactor Mission: "Yes, We Found Water!"|last=Lakdawalla|first=Emily|date=2009-11-13|publisher=The Planetary Society|accessdate=2010-04-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122233405/http://www.planetary.org/news/2009/1113_LCROSS_Lunar_Impactor_Mission_Yes_We.html|archivedate=2010-01-22}}</ref><ref name="Colaprete">{{Cite journal|last=Colaprete|first=A.|coauthors=Ennico, K.; Wooden, D.; Shirley, M.; Heldmann, J.; Marshall, W.; Sollitt, L.; Asphaug, E.; Korycansky, D.; Schultz, P.; Hermalyn, B.; Galal, K.; Bart, G. D.; Goldstein, D.; Summy, D.|date=March 1–5, 2010|title=Water and More: An Overview of LCROSS Impact Results|journal=41st Lunar and Planetary Science Conference|volume=41|issue=1533|pages=2335|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2010LPI....41.2335C|access-date=2011-02-02|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707200956/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2010LPI....41.2335C|dead-url=no}}</re